data.description: Come check out this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home located in Silver Spring Shores. This home is conveniently located with easy access to Maricamp road, Publix, Walmart, and more. Home features a large primary bedroom along with a fenced in backyard and screened in back porch. Solar panels reduce power bill. Tenant occupied until January 28th 2025. Call for your showing today!
